                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h3 class="subheading">3. Interior Features</h3>
                <p>Step inside the Kia Syros, and you’re greeted with a spacious, luxurious cabin. The SUV is equipped with plush leather seats, ambient lighting, and a customizable infotainment system. Key features include a 10.25-inch touchscreen display, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and wireless charging. With ample legroom and cargo space, the Syros ensures comfort for long journeys and daily commutes alike.</p>
                <div class="row m-b20">
