                <h3 class="subheading">6. Fuel Efficiency</h3>
                <p>The Kia Syros delivers impressive fuel efficiency, making it an economical choice for daily drivers. The petrol variant provides an average mileage of 18 km/l, while the diesel engine offers up to 22 km/l, depending on driving conditions. These figures ensure that the Syros is both environmentally friendly and cost-effective.</p>
                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h3 class="subheading">7. Pricing and Variants</h3>
                <p>The Kia Syros is available in multiple trims to suit diverse budgets and needs. Here’s a breakdown of the pricing:</p>
                <ul>
